{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01KY5rRWNc3JYS5KmcuXA7zi","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the current state:\n\n**Current permissions on /app:**\n- `app-user`: configure=\"\" (EMPTY!), write=\".*\", read=\".*\" — missing configure permission\n- `ops-user`: configure=\".*\", write=\".*\", read=\".*\" — should NOT be on /app at all\n- `admin`: configure=\".*\", write=\".*\", read=\".*\" — fine\n\n**Current permissions on /ops:**\n- `admin`: configure=\".*\", write=\".*\", read=\".*\" — fine\n- `ops-user`: has NO permissions on /ops at all — missing entirely\n\n**Required end state:**\n- `app-user`: full configure/write/read on /app, NO permissions on /ops\n- `ops-user`: full configure/write/read on /ops, NO permissions on /app\n\nI need to make three changes: grant `app-user` the missing configure permission on /app, remove `ops-user` from /app entirely, and add `ops-user` to /ops with full permissions. I'll use rabbitmqctl commands to execute these fixes.\n\nExecuting the permission updates...","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":893,"cache_read_input_tokens":28793,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":893},"output_tokens":13,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c489259a-0236-49e7-b1ce-5ff0d0d76935","uuid":"206c7034-e736-49e7-b963-c229b4de5fa2","request_id":"req_011CcdguE6PR8RtGhnCsLQwh"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01KY5rRWNc3JYS5KmcuXA7zi","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The issues are clear:\n- `app-user` on `/app`: configure is empty (should be `.*`)\n- `ops-user` is on `/app` with full perms (should NOT be)\n- `ops-user` has zero permissions on `/ops` (should have full perms)\n- `app-user` has no permissions on `/ops` (already correct — nothing to clean)\n\nFixing all three in one shot:"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":893,"cache_read_input_tokens":28793,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":893},"output_tokens":13,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c489259a-0236-49e7-b1ce-5ff0d0d76935","uuid":"0941ccc1-8e6e-423c-896e-c52a1b2621ad","request_id":"req_011CcdguE6PR8RtGhnCsLQwh"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01KY5rRWNc3JYS5KmcuXA7zi","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01KvKW2aBLHdS7om15RL3r24","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"NS=\"karma-rabbitmq-failover-first-01-2026-cf1c63a4-cluster-a\"\n\n# Fix app-user on /app — add missing configure permission\nkubectl -n $NS exec rabbitmq-0 -- rabbitmqctl set_permissions -p /app app-user \".*\" \".*\" \".*\"\n\n# Remove ops-user from /app entirely\nkubectl -n $NS exec rabbitmq-0 -- rabbitmqctl clear_permissions -p /app ops-user\n\n# Give ops-user full permissions on /ops\nkubectl -n $NS exec rabbitmq-0 -- rabbitmqctl set_permissions -p /ops ops-user \".*\" \".*\" \".*\"","description":"Fix RabbitMQ user permissions"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":893,"cache_read_input_tokens":28793,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":893},"output_tokens":13,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c489259a-0236-49e7-b1ce-5ff0d0d76935","uuid":"644d2502-d1ff-402c-b5d0-b185cde5c989","request_id":"req_011CcdguE6PR8RtGhnCsLQwh"}
